9", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75411992_840760134529292_4741404782520524397_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rEYAfD4tUuIQ7kNvgH9YGA5&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AkfBAtaSfyWegq_ecSDFFd4&oh=00_AYC8fDelMiEkBtO2IcbSWnLm8ru7YgkqP_fyxVvYZr4lkQ&oe=66F6A6B7"}, {"file_name": "vlcsnap-00008.png", "id": "7282727451839924", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035307_7282727458506590_4830324704851622877_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=nYOlViXFCrwQ7kNvgHYYp7L&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AkfBAtaSfyWegq_ecSDFFd4&oh=00_AYBPEUFK6SIce45Qeat-PHR6YnVa5303V8Onl6yF8l2oUQ&oe=66F6A32E"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "landscapefull3.png", "id": "1181005139718728", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036670_1181005143052061_709758329527305958_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=65iKe-sLJskQ7kNvgGjoi-J&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AkfBAtaSfyWegq_ecSDFFd4&oh=00_AYAqJq85fIkYh-wQPsqSW_uE-LR1y518ihLWw0AShsaLaw&oe=66F69DF2"}, "display_name": "3D Mahjong worlds - Quest", "keywords": ["strategy", "mahjong", "board", "relax", "classic"], "long_description": "This is the VR implementation of the classic Mahjong game\n\nWhether you are a mahjong master or a beginner, this game will be your best choice!\nCreative design of solid 3D mahjong levels, and simple game rules, suitable for everyone!\nIt\u2019s transformed from the traditional matching game and brings a relaxing experience to players in a 3D way.\nBe the master and pair all the cubes to eliminate them on over 30 levels!\n\nGame features:\n\n- 30 levels\n- Classic and 3D style levels.\n- Rotate, move and zoom the board.\n- English, Hungarian and Simplified Chinese languages.\n- Relaxing environment.\n", "short_description": "This is the VR implementation of the classic Mahjong game\n\nNo matter if you are a mahjong master or a beginner, this game will be your best choice!\nC